her (novel)|The Watcher]]'' || [[Ace Books]]\n!style=\"text-align:center; background-color:transparent;\"| <ref name=\"Loc82\"/>\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background:#B0C4DE;\" |{{sort|19831|[[1982 in literature|1983]]}}\n| {{sortname|James P.|Hogan|James P. Hogan (writer)}}* || ''[[Voyage from Yesteryear]]'' || [[Del Rey Books]]\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#B0C4DE;\"| <ref name=\"Loc83\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent;\" |{{sort|19832|[[1982 in literature|1983]]}}\n| {{sortname|Ann|Maxwell}} || ''[[Fire Dancer]]'' || [[New American Library]]\n!style=\"text-align:center; background-color:transparent;\"| <ref name=\"Loc83\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent;\" |{{sort|19833|[[1982 in literature|1983]]}}\n| {{sortname|Robert A.|Heinlein}} || ''[[Friday (novel)|Friday]]'' || [[Henry Holt and Company|Holt, Rinehart and Winston]]\n!style=\"text-align:center; background-color:transparent;\"| <ref name=\"Loc83\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent;\" |{{sort|19834|[[1982 in literature|1983]]}}\n| {{sortname|Julian|May}} || ''[[The Many-Colored Land]]'' || [[Houghton Mifflin Harcourt|Houghton Mifflin]]\n!style=\"text-align:center; background-color:transparent;\"| <ref name=\"Loc83\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent;\" |{{sort|19835|[[1981 in literature|1983]]}}\n| {{sortname|Larry|Niven}} and {{sortname|Jerry|Pournelle}} || ''[[Oath of Fealty (novel)|Oath of Fealty]]'' || [[Phantasia Press]]\n!style=\"text-align:center; background-color:transparent;\"| <ref name=\"Loc83\"/>\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background:#B0C4DE;\" |{{sort|19841|[[1983 in literature|1984]]